data.description: Explore this exquisite and spacious townhome nestled in the picturesque Orchards section of the highly sought-after Farm Subdivision in Carolina Forest. This inviting home is ready for you to move in and make your own, showcasing 4 spacious bedrooms, including a main level primary suite, and 2.5 well-appointed bathrooms. The kitchen boasts elegant quartz countertops with a sleek glass backsplash, complemented by a brand-new set of appliances and an island for added functionality. Additionally, French doors with integrated blinds lead to the heated and cooled all-seasons room where you can enjoy the serene pond views. A brand new HVAC system has been installed, as well as electric blinds in the upstairs loft. Revel in the beautifully landscaped and well-maintained neighborhood, which grants access to pools and other amenities. The location couldn't be more ideal, ensuring effortless and quick access to International Drive, River Oaks Drive, and Carolina Forest Boulevard. A must-see property that will leave you in awe. Don't wait. Schedule your private tour today!
